          "id": "11.2",
          "title": "Oral Care for Unconscious Patients",
          "content": "### 11.2 Oral Care for Unconscious Patients\n\n**Before oral care:** Assess the **gag reflex** — absence increases aspiration risk.\n\n**Technique:** Lateral position; suction available; small amounts of liquid; foam swabs or soft toothbrush.\n\n---"
